E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Our couples move in together and adjust to married life. Sparks fly at the dinner party, when two brides give less-than-glowing reviews of their hubbies... awks! (S10 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: At the first Commitment Ceremony, some couples celebrate their success so far. But as two couples clash, one bride's bad-mouthing lands her in hot water. (S10 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: It's Experts Week, and time for our newly-weds to strengthen their marriages. And it's married at first spice for some, thanks to Charlene's intimacy workshop! (S10 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Romantic confessions are on the menu at the second dinner party, and one bride questions her marriage when she struggles to find validation from her husband. (S10 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hotel Transylvania

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Lego Masters Australia
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Grand Finale: It's the USA vs Germany vs Australia as the top three teams leave no brick unturned in the battle for global glory. Who'll win the $100,000? (S6 Ep12/12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Day After Tomorrow
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2004) Tense sci-fi thriller starring Jake Gyllenhaal and Dennis Quaid. A scientist sets out to save his son when global warming plunges the world into a sudden climatic catastrophe.

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: At the commitment ceremony, some relationships blossom like their wedding bouquets. But for others, there's communication calamity and a 'do-I-stay?' dilemma. (S10 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: MAFS UK: It's Official!...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...With Lucinda Light: Brand new series - David Potts, expert Charlene and bride Sarah join Lucinda, as things hot up for Experts Week. Did an intimacy workshop spice things up? (S3 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Virgin Island

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks Omnibus

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Tony's plea hearing takes shocking twists and turns, while Dodger comes across some damning evidence. And Vicky wants to know what really happened to Robbie...

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Clare sets out for revenge, while the walls close in on Jez. And a resident is determined to end their family's reign of destruction.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Proton Resurgence: Leonard and Sheldon hire Professor Proton, the host of a TV science show they watched as children, to come to their flat and entertain them. (S6 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Anxiety Optimization: When Sheldon gets stuck in a rut with his research, he asks his friends to cure his mental block by raising his stress levels. (S8 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
